# Strategy notebook — `days.md` date semantics (anti-split)

**SSOT:** [STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md — `days.md` date keys](../../docs/skill-work/work-strategy/strategy-notebook/STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md#days-md-date-semantics).

**Invariants (WORK / `strategy` / **EOD compose**):**

- **`## YYYY-MM-DD` in `days.md`** = **compose / continuity day** (default: **end-of-day strategy session**), not proof the operator uploaded files that calendar day.
- **Do not** add a **new** `## YYYY-MM-DD` **only** because **`Accumulator for:`**, inbox **`### … YYYY-MM-DD`**, assistant session clock, or **wire bylines** differ — consolidate; put external dates in **Links** / **Signal**; optional **compose date note** (legacy: **weave date note**) when scopes differ.
- **Operator last-ingest boundary** → fold assistant work into that **notebook day** (or episodic heading), not extra split headings.
- **`STATUS.md`** links must match **real** `days.md` anchors after consolidation.

**EOD page-shape menu** (options before editing `days.md` in the **EOD strategy session**) — [architecture § EOD compose — page-shape menu](../../docs/skill-work/work-strategy/strategy-notebook/STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md#weave-command-page-shape-menu). *Legacy:* “Weave menu.”
